name: Create a static patient and verify this patient in mobile caregiver app

steps.name: When I hover on the "Dashboard-All Patient" tab
When I click the Manage Patients option
Then Search and delete duplicate user Patient_Auto_Test
When I hover on the "Dashboard-All Patient" tab
When I click the Add A New Patient option
When I fill Patient_Auto_Test data in baby first name field
When I fill Ben data in baby last name field
When I fill Male data in gender field
When I fill Default data in hospital or office field
When I fill testcaregiver 2may (testcaregiver2may@yopmail.com) (+1 1987654356) data in caregiver field
When I fill Hospital / Clinic data in treatment Location field
When I click on the button with text Generate Firstday Healthcare Medical Record Number
Then QR code should be generated and First day Healthcare Medical Record Number should be generated
When I click on the button with text Save
Then Success message Patient Added Succesfully! appears
Then A "New Patient" gets created And it is displayed on the "My Patient list" with Patient_Auto_Test and Ben and RPM,TELEMED,EMR and Discharge and <hospitalLocation> and Active
